     "constraints": { "max_files": N, "forbidden_paths": [] },
     "validation": ["<node_command>"]
   }

4. Capsule (The Result)
   - Only on success. Reference Gene used.
   {
     "type": "Capsule",
     "schema_version": "1.5.0",
     "id": "capsule_<timestamp>",
